根据[[篮球|篮球]]比赛规则，球队可以通过球员投篮和[[罚球_(篮球)|罚球]][[得分_(篮球)|得分]]，最终得分高的球队赢得比赛<ref>{{Cite_web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306085721/http://www.fiba.com/pages/eng/fc/baskbasi/glos.asp | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | url = http://www.fiba.com/pages/eng/fc/baskBasi/glos.asp | title = Basketball glossary | work = FIBA.com | accessdate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。'''{{lang|en|[[NBA|NBA]]}}得分王'''是指每个{{lang|en|NBA}}赛季平均每场比赛得分最多的球员。[[1968-69_NBA赛季|1968-69年赛季]]前，得分王都是全季得分最多的球员，之后再改为平均每场比赛得分最多的球员<ref name="scoring title">{{Cite_news | accessdate = 2016-08-06 | date = 2006-01-15 | first = Liz | last = Robbins | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425003212/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9402E4DF143FF936A25752C0A9609C8B63 | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9402E4DF143FF936A25752C0A9609C8B63 | title = Around the N.B.A.; In the N.B.A., Scoring Titles Rarely Equal Championships | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2016-04-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。另外，由于三分球是在[[1979-80_NBA赛季|1979-80年赛季]]首次引入，所以此前的得分王没有三分球数据<ref>{{Cite_web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1990/02/05/sports/3-pointer-adds-dimension-to-nba.html | title = 3-Pointer Adds Dimension To N.B.A | newspaper = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | accessdate = 2016-08-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308034951/http://www.nytimes.com/1990/02/05/sports/3-pointer-adds-dimension-to-nba.html | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | date = 1990-02-05 | first = Clifton | last = Brown }}</ref><ref>{{Cite_web | url = http://assets.espn.go.com/nba/s/2003/0102/1485892.html | title = The trey is the thing in today's NBA | work = ESPN.com | publisher = ESPN Internet Ventures | accessdate = 2016-08-06 | date = 2003-01-02 | first = Mark | last = Haubner | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171732/http://assets.espn.go.com/nba/s/2003/0102/1485892.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。从[[1974-75_NBA赛季|1974-75年赛季]]开始，争夺得分王头衔的球员在相应赛季要参加全部82场比赛中的至少70场，或是得分不低于1400<ref name="ratereq">{{Cite_web | archivedate = 2016-03-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322071215/http://www.basketball-reference.com/about/rate_stat_req.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.basketball-reference.com/about/rate_stat_req.html | title = Rate Statistic Requirements | publisher = Sports Reference LLC | work = basketball-reference.com | accessdate = 2016-07-24 }}</ref>。[[威尔特·张伯伦|威尔特·张伯伦]]在[[1961-62_NBA賽季|1961–62年赛事]]共获得4029分，场均得分50.4，两项都创下历史纪录并保持至今<ref name="chamberlain_bio">{{Cite_web | url = http://www.nba.com/history/players/chamberlain_bio.html | title = Wilt Chamberlain | work = NBA.com | publisher = Turner Sports Interactive, Inc | accessdate = 2016-08-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160509143116/http://www.nba.com/history/players/chamberlain_bio.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-05-09 }}</ref>。他在[[1959-60_NBA赛季|1959–60年赛季]]平均每场比赛得到37.6分，至今保持着新手球员的最高纪录<ref name="chamberlain_bio" />。[[凯文·杜兰特|凯文·杜兰特]]在[[2013-14_NBA賽季|2013–14赛季]]共得到2593分，平均每场比赛32分，是现役球员中的得分王。

[[迈克尔·乔丹|迈克尔·乔丹]]共有十次获得分王称号，比其他球员都多<ref name="jordan_bio">{{Cite_web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160623222153/http://www.nba.com/history/players/jordan_bio.html | work = NBA.com | url = http://www.nba.com/history/players/jordan_bio.html | title = Michael Jordan | publisher = Turner Sports Interactive, Inc | accessdate = 2016-08-06 | archivedate = 2016-06-23 }}</ref>。乔丹和张伯伦均曾连续七次获得分王头衔，是连庄次数最多的球员（张伯伦一共也是七次获得分王称号）<ref name="jordan_bio" />。[[乔治·格温|乔治·格温]]、[[艾伦·艾佛森|艾伦·艾佛森]]和[[凯文·杜兰特|凯文·杜兰特]]都曾四次当选得分王<ref>{{Cite_web | url = http://www.nba.com/sixers/features/iverson_050420.html | title = Iverson Wins Fourth Scoring Title | work = NBA.com | publisher = Turner Sports Interactive, Inc | accessdate = 2014-04-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140419040639/http://www.nba.com/sixers/features/iverson_050420.html | date = 2005-04-20 | first = Brian | last = Smith | archivedate = 2014-04-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，[[乔治·迈肯|乔治·迈肯]]、[[尼尔·约翰斯顿|尼尔·约翰斯顿]]、[[鲍伯·麦卡杜|鲍伯·麦卡杜]]和[[詹姆士·哈登|詹姆士·哈登]]各有三次。[[保罗·阿里金|保罗·阿里金]]、[[鲍勃·佩蒂特|鲍勃·佩蒂特]]、[[卡里姆·阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔|卡里姆·阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔]]、[[沙奎尔·奥尼尔|沙奎尔·奥尼尔]]、[[特雷西·麦克格雷迪|特雷西·麦克格雷迪]]和[[科比·布莱恩特|科比·布莱恩特]]都曾两度当选得分王。历史上共有五位球员在同一赛季拿下得分王头衔的同时还带领球队赢得[[NBA总冠军列表|总冠军]]，分别是[[乔·福尔克斯|乔·福尔克斯]]于[[1947年BAA总决赛|1947年]]带领[[金州勇士|费城勇士]]打入决赛、迈肯于[[1949年BAA总决赛|1949]]和[[1950年NBA总决赛|1950年]]率领[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]进入决赛，阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔于[[1971年NBA总决赛|1971年]]同[[密尔沃基雄鹿|密尔沃基雄鹿]]打进决赛，乔丹于[[1991年NBA总决赛|1991]]至[[1993年NBA总决赛|1993年]]和[[1996年NBA总决赛|1996]]至[[1998年NBA总决赛|1998年]]率[[芝加哥公牛|芝加哥公牛]]冲进决赛，奥尼尔于[[2000年NBA总决赛|2000年]]带领[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]进入决赛<ref name="scoring title" /><ref>{{Cite_news | first = Janis | last = Carr | title = Jackson aware of the score with O'Neal | newspaper = The Orange County Register | publisher = Freedom Communications, Inc | page = D11 | date = 2000-04-02}}</ref>。自引入三分球制以来，只有奥尼尔在拿下得分王的赛季没有投进过三分球<ref name="oneal" />。

杜兰特在[[2009-10_NBA赛季|2009-10年赛季]]平均每场得到30.1分，获得分王头衔时还只出生21年197天，是{{lang|en|NBA}}历史上最年轻的得分王<ref name="youngest">{{Cite_news | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory?id=10378942 | title = Durant Becomes NBA's Youngest Scoring Champ | first = Jeff | last = Latzke | date = 2010-04-15 | work = ABC News | publisher = ABC News Internet Ventures | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110217173028/http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory?id=10378942 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2011-02-17 | archivedate = 2011-02-17 }}</ref>。

